{"tid":2162683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天瑞邨男子高處墮下 當場命殞","createTime":"2020-08-18T08:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T09:02:06.000Z","uid":82394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed8a00e9d1a8c64c429cdb5bcbebeca1ec71451","tid":2162683,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:52:37.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】天水圍天瑞邨今早有男子從高處墮下，當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n有保安報警指，今早10時42分聞巨響前往查看，發現一名年約20歲男子倒臥瑞國樓簷篷上，疑由高處墮下，警員及救護員到場，證實男子已傷重當場死亡。警方正調查男子身份及墮下原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線（多種語言）︰28960000<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線（24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務）：24667350<br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%e5%a4%a9%e7%91%9e%e9%82%a8%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e9%ab%98%e8%99%95%e5%a2%ae%e4%b8%8b-%e7%95%b6%e5%a0%b4%e5%91%bd%e6%ae%9e-045600933.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e7%2591%259e%25e9%2582%25a8%25e7%2594%25b7%25e5%25ad%2590%25e9%25ab%2598%25e8%2599%2595%25e5%25a2%25ae%25e4%25b8%258b-%25e7%2595%25b6%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e5%2591%25bd%25e6%25ae%259e-045600933.html&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=46151a85\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%e5%a4%a9%e7%91%9e%e9%82%a8%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e9%ab%98%e8%99%95%e5%a2%ae%e4%b8%8b-%e7%95%b6%e5%a0%b4%e5%91%bd%e6%ae%9e-045600933.html</a>"},{"pid":"136afd0b642757b73e1c452939a2ba683e824124","tid":2162683,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a2cf314e5d67aeecc1d30d931385941417dd1e","tid":2162683,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=